<view class="container formal-page">
  <view class="card section intro-card">
    <view class="intro-badge">轻松换上正式穿搭</view>
    <view class="title-xl intro-title">一键换装</view>
    <view class="text-muted intro-desc">帮你把照片换成更正式的穿搭，报名照、证件照和职业资料都更省心。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card section option-card">
    <view class="title-md">选择想要的风格</view>
    <view class="text-muted option-desc">整体做成轻量、清爽的选择体验，不像后台表单。</view>

    <view class="option-group">
      <view class="option-label">性别</view>
      <view class="pill-row">
        <view
          wx:for="{{genderOptions}}"
          wx:key="value"
          class="pill {{gender === item.value ? 'pill-active' : ''}}"
          data-value="{{item.value}}"
          bindtap="handleGenderChange"
        >{{item.label}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="option-group">
      <view class="option-label">风格</view>
      <view class="style-list">
        <view
          wx:for="{{styleOptions}}"
          wx:key="value"
          class="style-card {{style === item.value ? 'style-card-active' : ''}}"
          data-value="{{item.value}}"
          bindtap="handleStyleChange"
        >
          <view class="style-title-row">
            <view class="style-title">{{item.label}}</view>
            <view class="style-check">{{style === item.value ? '已选' : ''}}</view>
          </view>
          <view class="text-muted style-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="option-group option-group-last">
      <view class="option-label">颜色</view>
      <view class="pill-row">
        <view
          wx:for="{{colorOptions}}"
          wx:key="value"
          class="pill color-pill {{color === item.value ? 'pill-active' : ''}}"
          data-value="{{item.value}}"
          bindtap="handleColorChange"
        >{{item.label}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card section upload-card">
    <view class="title-md">上传照片</view>
    <view class="text-muted upload-tip">建议上传正面、清晰、肩膀尽量完整的照片，换装效果会更自然。</view>

    <view class="upload-box {{imagePath ? 'upload-box-filled' : ''}}" bindtap="handleUploadBoxTap">
      <block wx:if="{{imagePath}}">
        <image class="upload-preview" src="{{imagePath}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
        <view class="upload-overlay">
          <view class="upload-file-name">{{imageName}}</view>
          <view class="upload-reselect">重新选择</view>
        </view>
      </block>
      <block wx:else>
        <view class="upload-illustration">
          <view class="upload-head"></view>
          <view class="upload-body"></view>
          <view class="upload-arrow"></view>
        </view>
        <view class="upload-title">上传一张清晰正面照</view>
        <view class="text-muted upload-copy">支持相册上传或直接拍摄，建议面部完整、无遮挡。</view>
      </block>
    </view>

    <view class="upload-action-row">
      <view class="upload-action ghost-action" catchtap="chooseFromAlbum">从相册上传</view>
      <view class="upload-action primary-action" catchtap="chooseFromCamera">拍一张试试</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{generating}}" class="card section processing-card">
    <view class="processing-top">
      <view class="processing-ring">{{processingStep}}</view>
      <view>
        <view class="title-md">处理中</view>
        <view class="text-muted processing-desc">{{processingText}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="processing-track">
      <view class="processing-bar processing-bar-step-{{processingStep}}"></view>
    </view>
    <view class="processing-note">换装仍然通过 server 接口封装对接；若接口暂未就绪，会展示清晰占位结果，不影响当前主链路。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section submit-section">
    <primary-button text="立即生成" loading="{{generating}}" bind:tap="handleGenerate"></primary-button>
    <view class="text-muted submit-tip">提交后会先显示处理中状态，再进入结果展示页。</view>
  </view>
</view>
